;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Son cr&eacute;ateur Gary CRAIG met sa d&eacute;couverte &agrave; la port&eacute;e de tous et gratuitement.&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.technique-eft.com/gary-craig\">http://www.technique-eft.com/gary-craig</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<h2>En quoi l&rsquo;EFT est-il efficace?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nEn tout ! Si tout est d&eacute;sordre ou d&eacute;s&eacute;quilibre &eacute;nerg&eacute;tique, le tapotement est efficace dans la r&eacute;solution d&rsquo;un grand nombre de probl&egrave;mes.<br />\r\nOn peut citer tous les sentiments&rdquo; n&eacute;gatifs&rdquo; ou &ldquo;difficiles&rdquo; comme l&rsquo;anxi&eacute;t&eacute;, les crises de panique,<br />\r\nl&rsquo;amertume,les regrets, la col&egrave;re, la honte, le manque de confiance, tous les chagrins, tous<br />\r\nles mal-&ecirc;tre.<br />\r\nToutes nos croyances restrictives, nos addictions, les souvenirs traumatisants, les phobies...<br />\r\nEt bien entendu, sur nos maux physiques.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Par qui et comment ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nL&rsquo;apprentissage du tapotement et des s&eacute;quences &agrave; suivre sont tr&egrave;s simples et rapides,<br />\r\net accessible &agrave; tous. Allez voir les videos de <strong>EFT</strong> en fran&ccedil;ais et vous deviendrez tr&egrave;s rapidement<br />\r\nautonome.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Des r&eacute;sultats ?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nLes r&eacute;sultats sont imm&eacute;diats et remplac&eacute;s par une profonde s&eacute;r&eacute;nit&eacute; dans bien des cas.<br />\r\nChaque probl&egrave;me &agrave; plusieurs aspects et il se peut que tous les aspects ne soient pas abord&eacute;s<br />\r\nlors d&rsquo;une s&eacute;ance parceque m&eacute;connus de la personne.<br />\r\nLorsqu&rsquo;ils se pr&eacute;sentent, on traite ce nouvel aspect pour une r&eacute;solution plus en profondeur.<br />\r\nIl suffit d&rsquo;une s&eacute;quence ou deux pour les &eacute;liminer.</p>','<h2>Put some sunshine in your life</h2>\r\n\r\n<h1>E.F.T.</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>A new method of treatment called <strong>EFT </strong>(Emotional Freedom Techniques)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We talk about:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Psychological acupuncture</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Meridian Therapy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tapping Therapy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tapping is the light tapping with the fingertips on certain acupuncture points.<br />\r\nTheir number varies according to the techniques used. For<strong> EFT</strong>, energy blockages or negative thoughts lead to an evil being, physical or emotional pain; tapping up these blockages and resulting in a large immediate well-being and lifted problems accompanying these imbalances.<br />\r\nEase of use of <strong>EFT</strong> in fact his great fame as a single sequence is used to treat any problems whatsoever.<br />\r\nIts creator Gary CRAIG puts his discovery to everyone and free of charge.<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.technique-eft.com/gary-craig\">http://www.technique-eft.com/gary-craig</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><br />\r\nWhat EFT is effective?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nIn all! If everything is energy imbalance or disorder, pat is effective in solving many problems.<br />\r\nWe can quote all the &quot;negative&quot; feelings or &quot;difficult&quot; as anxiety, panic attacks,<br />\r\nbitterness, regret, anger, shame, lack of confidence, all the sorrows, all<br />\r\nthe discomfort.<br />\r\nAll restrictive beliefs, addictions, traumatic memories, phobias ...<br />\r\nAnd of course, our physical ailments.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>By whom and how?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nLearning and tapping sequences to follow are very simple and quick,<br />\r\nand accessible to all. Check out videos of <strong>EFT</strong> in French and you will become very quickly<br />\r\nindependently.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Results?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nThe results are immediate and replaced by a deep serenity in many cases.<br />\r\nEvery problem in several aspects and